<p style="text-align:justify;"><span class="AddHand-editors">[In pencil; on upper right of page]</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;">Looked through this<br />parcel Nov<sup>r</sup> 2<sup>d</sup> 1841<br />R McKenzie<br />nothing in it</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;"><span class="AddHand-editors">[In ink]</span></p>
<p class="head">Journal</p>
<p></p>
<p class="head">Du Fort Kamanaitiquoya</p>
<p></p>
<p class="head">A la</p>
<p></p>
<p class="head">Riviere de Montreal</p>
<p></p>
<p class="head">Par</p>
